  <brief_title>High Dose of Activated Recombinant Human Factor VII for Treatment of Mild/Moderate Joint Bleeds in Haemophilia Patients With Inhibitors</brief_title>
  <official_title>rFVIIa (NovoSeven®) for Treatment of Mild/Moderate Joint Bleeds in Haemophilia Patients With Inhibitors: A Double-blind Study of a Single High Dose Versus Standard Multiple Doses of rFVIIa</official_title>
  <sponsors>
