  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is conducted in Europe. The aim of this trial is to evaluate the efficacy and
      safety of two dose schedules of activated recombinant human factor VII in treatment of joint
      bleeds in haemophilia patients with inhibitors.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
